{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-tsx","path":"/javascript-built-in-function/","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<h2>자바스크립트 내장 함수</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>내장함수 정의</p>\n<p>자바스크립트에서 자체적으로 제공하는 함수로, alert() 함수와 prompt()등이 있다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>타이머 함수</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>메서드 이름</th>\n<th>설명</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>setTimeout(function, millisecond)</td>\n<td>일정 시간 후 함수를 한번 실행함</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>setInterval(function, millisecond)</td>\n<td>일정 시간마다 함수를 반복 실행함</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>clearTimeout(id)</td>\n<td>해당 id의 setTimeout 함수 중지</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>clearInterval(id)</td>\n<td>해당 id의 setInterval 함수 중지</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>setTimeout() 함수는 한번만 실행하므로 특별히 주의할 사항이 없지만 setInterval() 함수는 지속적으로 컴퓨터의 자원을 소비하므로 꼭 중지시켜 주어야 함</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// 1초마다 함수 실행</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> intervalID <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">setInterval</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n\t<span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'1초 경과'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">1000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 10초 뒤에 함수 실행</span>\r\n<span class=\"token function\">setTimeout</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n\t<span class=\"token function\">clearInterval</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>intervalID<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">10000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>setTimeout() 함수와 setInterval()함수를 사용하면 타이머 아이디를 리턴하는데, 이 아이디를 clearTimeout()함수나 clearInterval()함수의 매개변수에 넣어주면 타이머를 정지할 수 있다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>인코딩, 디코딩 함수</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>함수 이름</th>\n<th>설명</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>escape()</td>\n<td>알파벳, 숫자, 일부 특수문자(@ * - _ + . /)를 제외하고 모두 인코딩함.<br>1바이트 문자는 %XX, 2바이트 문자는 %uXXXX 형태로 변환</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>unescape()</td>\n<td>위 함수의 디코딩 버전</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>encodeURI(uri)</td>\n<td>escape()함수에서 인터넷 주소에 사용되는 일부 특수문자(: ; / = ? &#x26;)는 변환하지 않음</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>decodeURI(encodedURI)</td>\n<td>위 함수의 디코딩 버전</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>encodeURIComponent(uriComponent)</td>\n<td>알파벳, 숫자를 제외한 모든 문자를 인코딩함.<br>UTF-8 인코딩과 동일</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>decodeURIComponent(encodedURI)</td>\n<td>위 함수의 디코딩 버전</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>모두 비슷한 기능을 수행하므로 어떤것을 사용해도 상관 없다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>코드 실행 함수</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>함수 이름</th>\n<th>설명</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>eval(string)</td>\n<td>문자열을 자바스크립트 코드로 실행함</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> willEval <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">''</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\nwillEval <span class=\"token operator\">+=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'var number = 10;'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\nwillEval <span class=\"token operator\">+=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'alert(number);'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token function\">eval</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>willEval<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 10</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>number<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 10</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>eval() 함수는 문자열을 자바스크립트 코드로 실행하는 함수이므로 eval() 함수로 실행된 코드에서 정의한 변수를 활용할 수도 있다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>숫자 확인 함수</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>함수 이름</th>\n<th>설명</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>isFinite(number)</td>\n<td>number가 유한한 값인지 확인</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>isNaN(number)</td>\n<td>number가 NaN인지 확인</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>자바스크립트는 숫자를 0으로 나누면 Infinity라는 값이 들어간다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> number <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>number <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">':'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token function\">isFinite</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>number<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// Infinity : false</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>또한 자바스크립트에는 Infinity라는 변수가 존재하지만, 음수를 0으로 나누면 -Infinity가 되므로 Infinity 변수와 비교하지 말고 반드시 isFinite() 함수를 사용해야 한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> number <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>number <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> <span class=\"token number\">Infinity</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// false</span>\r\n<span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>number <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">Infinity</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// true</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">isFinite</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>number<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// false</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>NaN도 마찬가지로 NaN 이라는 변수가 존재하지만 NaN끼리 비교하는 것은 불가하므로 반드시 isNaN() 함수로 확인해야한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">NaN</span> <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> <span class=\"token number\">NaN</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// false</span>\r\n<span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">isNaN</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">NaN</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// true</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>숫자 변환 함수</p>\n<p>자바스크립트는 Number() 함수 외에도 또 다른 숫자 변환 함수를 제공한다.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>함수 이름</th>\n<th>설명</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>parseInt(string)</td>\n<td>문자열을 정수로 변환</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>parseFloat(string)</td>\n<td>문자열을 유리수로 변환</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>Number() 함수는 인자에 숫자로 바꿀수 없는 부분이 하나라도 있으면 NaN으로 변환하지만, 위의 두가지 함수는 숫자로 변환할 수 있는 부분까지는 모두 숫자로 변환한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> won <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'1000원'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> dollar <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'1.5$'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">Number</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>won<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">':'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token function\">Number</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>dollar<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// NaN:NaN</span>\r\n<span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">parseInt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>won<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">':'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token function\">parseInt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>dollar<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 1000:1</span>\r\n<span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">parseFloat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>won<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">':'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token function\">parseFloat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>dollar<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 1000:1.5</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 앞부터 읽으므로 맨 앞에 숫자가 오지 않으면 변환 불가</span>\r\n<span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">parseInt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'$1000'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">':'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token function\">parseFloat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'$1000'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// NaN:NaN</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>parseInt()는 맨 처음에 0x로 시작하면 16진수로 생각하고 변환한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token function\">parseInt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'0x273'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 627</span>\r\n<span class=\"token function\">parseInt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'273'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 273</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token function\">parseFloat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'0x273'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 0</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>parseInt()함수의 두번째 매개변수에 진법을 입력하면 해당 진법의 수로 인식한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token function\">parseInt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'FF'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">16</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 255</span>\r\n<span class=\"token function\">parseInt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'52'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 52</span>\r\n<span class=\"token function\">parseInt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'11'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">8</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 9</span>\r\n<span class=\"token function\">parseInt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'10'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 2</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>parseFloat() 함수는 중간에 e가 들어가면 자릿수로 인식한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token function\">parseFloat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'52.273e5'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 5227300</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ol>","frontmatter":{"title":"[자바스크립트] 내장함수","summary":"자바스크립트 문법 공부","date":"2020.09.17.","categories":["Javascript"],"thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/e8f128e9bd3eed0ca6ff8bd817f96eb9/42055/javascript.jpg","srcSet":"/static/e8f128e9bd3eed0ca6ff8bd817f96eb9/ba9a6/javascript.jpg 200w,\n/static/e8f128e9bd3eed0ca6ff8bd817f96eb9/34e0f/javascript.jpg 400w,\n/static/e8f128e9bd3eed0ca6ff8bd817f96eb9/42055/javascript.jpg 800w","sizes":"(min-width: 800px) 800px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/e8f128e9bd3eed0ca6ff8bd817f96eb9/4c856/javascript.webp 200w,\n/static/e8f128e9bd3eed0ca6ff8bd817f96eb9/4dac1/javascript.webp 400w,\n/static/e8f128e9bd3eed0ca6ff8bd817f96eb9/d0f18/javascript.webp 800w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 800px) 800px, 100vw"}]},"width":800,"height":600}},"publicURL":"/static/e8f128e9bd3eed0ca6ff8bd817f96eb9/javascript.jpg"}}}}]}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/javascript-built-in-function/"}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}